result.name: 中興牛雜粉麵

reviews.text: Tasty beef brisket and offal noodles  for a measely $29 and add $4 more for a cold drink.   The place is inside a wet market but it is surprisingly clean for where it is.  Needless to said very popular with the locals and very crowded seating.  But at this price, who can't complain!
Nice service and good price
OK.
今日叫咗碗腩什米線，牛腸苦，牛肚黑，牛腩好似柴皮咁，食咗半碗走人。
牛腩,牛什質素高,好味道。坐位較 擠迫。
